---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Solutions" description="Automation engineering and SEO development — two practices, one engine. We build the systems that produce different results.">
  <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto py-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-7xl">Solutions</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl">
        We build two kinds of systems. Both are designed to run without you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Opening Statement -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-4 mb-10">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold italic text-foreground">
          "Every system is perfectly designed to get the results it gets."
        </p>
      </blockquote>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        <p>
          If your team is drowning in manual work, that's not a people problem — it's a systems problem. If your SEO isn't generating leads, that's not a content problem — it's an infrastructure problem.
        </p>
        <p>
          We build the systems that produce different results.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 mb-16">
      <a href="/solutions/automation" class="group rounded-lg border bg-card p-8 transition-all hover:bg-accent/50 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
          The Engine
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Automation Engineering</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          Every business has workflows that shouldn't be manual. Data entry, report generation, lead routing, system syncing, file processing — all of it can be automated.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          We build custom automation systems that connect your tools, eliminate busywork, and give your team clarity on what to work on next. Whether it's a single workflow or a full operational overhaul, we design systems that run on their own.
        </p>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary group-hover:underline">Explore Automation &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/solutions/seo" class="group rounded-lg border bg-card p-8 transition-all hover:bg-accent/50 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="mb-4 inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium rounded-full">
          The Application
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">SEO Development</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
          We don't do "SEO services." We build SEO systems — programmatic sites, content pipelines, and technical infrastructure designed to generate organic traffic at scale.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
          Every SEO system we build is an automation system first. That's why they scale where traditional SEO doesn't.
        </p>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary group-hover:underline">Explore SEO &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Individual Services -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">All Services</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">Automation</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Workflow Automation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Custom n8n/Make/Zapier workflows that connect your tools and automate repetitive processes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">Automation</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">AI Agent Development</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Purpose-built AI agents for classification, extraction, generation, and decision-making.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">Automation</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">System Integration</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Connecting the tools you already use into a single coherent system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">SEO</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Programmatic Site Development</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Data-driven sites designed to scale across markets, locations, or service categories.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">SEO</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Content System Design</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Structured content workflows that turn data into published, optimized content.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">SEO</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Technical SEO & Site Architecture</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Schema, speed, linking, crawlability — the foundation that makes content rank.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border bg-card p-6 md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-xs text-primary font-medium mb-1">SEO</p>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">Local SEO Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Multi-location SEO systems for businesses that need to rank in multiple markets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
